# Dual BayCom PR-Stack — merge into /etc/baycom/axports/axports (example also at /etc/baycom/axports/dual.snippet)
# Use with config/examples/baycom-pr.dual.ini (or modems a + b in site INI)
#
#   name    callsign   speed  paclen  window  description
cb0       N0CALL-0   1200   255     2       Modem A / bcsf0
cb1       N0CALL-1   1200   255     2       Modem B / bcsf1
